> there is one.  I would like to have it as a virtual disk if possible but 
> I can use an individual file type encryption if needed.  I have 124 Mb of 
> stuff I would like to encrypt in a drive but only 10Mb I NEED to 
> encrypt.  Please email me and if you can give me an ftp site which I can 
