Try Secure File System, sfs100.zip, which you should be able to get from
somewhere on ftp.informatik.uni-hamburg.de. If you can't find it, drop the
author, Peter Gutmann, a line on pgut1@cs.aukuni.ac.nz.

I, for one, would appreciate you posting of a summary of what you discover.

